						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone lying in Survey No. 361.</p>						

						<p>This undated epigraph may be assigned to the 9th century A.D. on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>The inscription is engraved in a confused manner. It seems to refer to Kaṇḍlūru.</p>						

